    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "The `allItems` template was removed in v3 in favor of [`connectHits`](https://www.algolia.com/doc/api-reference/widgets/hits/js/#connector) ([see migration guide](https://www.algolia.com/doc/guides/building-search-ui/upgrade-guides/js/?#options-4)). The same behavior can be achieved with [`connectInfiniteHits`](https://www.algolia.com/doc/api-reference/widgets/infinite-hits/js/#connector).",
